  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408120/extras/c56ae8a85993b4814446e5bec5456446.webp?t=1736852693\" width=42 height=33 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408120/extras/6ebb44dea6d41072d241bd4413119814.webp?t=1736852693\" width=42 height=33 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408120/extras/38f2d1b4418c5b8c26312c0ba26a2c29.webp?t=1736852693\" width=42 height=33 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408120/extras/ff688d2ec825087441391ea2a2590eb8.webp?t=1736852693\" width=42 height=33 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408120/extras/11dfbfab931ab354578369b185755604.webp?t=1736852693\" width=30 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Candy Factory is overtaken at night by Insects, Spiders, and Little Critters that completely take over the place.<br>Help our Bonbons reach the exit together through 5 different areas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ll progress by jumping, climbing, running, swimming, and dodging enemies that are out to cause trouble.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Video Game for the Whole Family, A Sweet Adventure</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump and dodge enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overcome obstacles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and discover the different areas of a factory</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bathe in coconut and swim in chocolate</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408120/extras/c56ae8a85993b4814446e5bec5456446.webp?t=1736852693\" width=42 height=33 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408120/extras/6ebb44dea6d41072d241bd4413119814.webp?t=1736852693\" width=42 height=33 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408120/extras/38f2d1b4418c5b8c26312c0ba26a2c29.webp?t=1736852693\" width=42 height=33 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408120/extras/ff688d2ec825087441391ea2a2590eb8.webp?t=1736852693\" width=42 height=33 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408120/extras/11dfbfab931ab354578369b185755604.webp?t=1736852693\" width=30 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Candy Factory is overtaken at night by Insects, Spiders, and Little Critters that completely take over the place.<br>Help our Bonbons reach the exit together through 5 different areas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ll progress by jumping, climbing, running, swimming, and dodging enemies that are out to cause trouble.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Video Game for the Whole Family, A Sweet Adventure</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump and dodge enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overcome obstacles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and discover the different areas of a factory</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bathe in coconut and swim in chocolate</p></li></ul>",
